*******************************************************************************
       Name: Peripheral Extension
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_SELF
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 17
 Wait Beats: 24
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: Your peripheral awareness returns to its normal range.
Acquisition:
   - Psionicist: level 19
Description:
   Peripheral Extension is a Psionicist sensory enhancement spell. The
   psionicist expands the range of their psionic perception beyond normal
   physiological limits, effectively granting enhanced night vision and
   improved peripheral awareness. The caster can see clearly in darkness
   and has a wider effective field of view.

   This is the Psionicist's version of infravision, derived from psionic
   amplification of sensory processing rather than enhanced biological
   heat detection. The extended peripheral awareness also improves the
   Psionicist's ability to detect hidden enemies approaching from the sides
   or behind, making them harder to surprise during combat. The spell is
   particularly valuable in dungeon environments with limited lighting.
*******************************************************************************
